data.title: Passport Renewal at FedEx Office in Sevierville, TN
data.meta_description: FedEx Office has partnered with RushMyPassport in Sevierville, TN to provide expedited passport services, including passport renewals, new passports, lost or stolen passports, child passports, and passport photos.
data.text:
FedEx Office and RushMyPassport™ have partnered to help travelers who need rush passport and travel visa services. If you are traveling soon and need to apply or renew your passport fast, get started online or visit your local FedEx Office for expedited passport options as fast as 3 business days!

Take advantage of convenient passport photos, overnight shipping, full-tracking visibility, and trusted travel advisors to help you through the process and avoid application delays. Just a few steps to get travel-ready quickly.

How It Works

Get started online with FedEx Office and RushMyPassport or by visiting your local FedEx Office in Sevierville. Select your passport type and processing speed. Once you place your expedited passport order, you will be guided through our online smart form to complete your application.

Next, print your application packet. This will include the required documents fully organized with all of the items you’ll need to submit for processing.
